Glad to do it. By the way, I also thought the MiniBox was well built
and had decent clarity. April and Alex were very gracious and sincere
in  demonstrating and explaining everything.

 And everyone that met you Frank was pleased to hear what you had to
say and as you witnessed, there are a few different ways people use
the Box. The attendees of the event that were not familiar with your 
Box seemed to get it almost right away. I think everyone who was there
appreciated you explaining the concept and it was great to see a group
of people seated up close to listen to you and your Box 25. No one was
rushing to leave the billiards room where you were set up even though
it was past 2 a.m. and most had been up all weekend. Thanks for
showing up! 
-Bill   

